<section class="mission">
  <div class="container mission-inner">
    <span class="mission-label" data-animate="fade-up">Our Purpose</span>
    <h2 class="mission-heading" data-animate="fade-up">
      Emerging technologies are a rare opportunity. Not a silver bullet, but the potential to intervene at the deepest levels of how power flows. Not just reimagining existing systems, but growing new ones alongside them.
    </h2>
    <div class="mission-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="mission-body-block" data-animate="fade-up">
      <p class="mission-body">
        Our current systems of coordination - how we organize, allocate resources, govern ourselves, make collective decisions - clearly aren't working for most people. Value is extracted rather than circulated, power ever more concentrated, our planet and people devastated.
      </p>
      <p class="mission-body">
        Meanwhile, across the world, there is a hidden mosaic of grassroots initiatives yearning to be woven. Open source, peer-to-peer, built to be forked.
      </p>
      <p class="mission-body">
        SuperBenefit is one part of a much larger regenerative ecosystem. Together, we are building the commons and cultivating the connective tissue between disparate communities, initiatives, technologies, and bioregions.
      </p>
      <p class="mission-body">
        Through projects like the Reimagining Power Project and All In For Sport, we work alongside partners across multiple continents, experimenting with decentralized tools to shift ownership and agency to communities that have been excluded from the systems that shape their lives.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mission {
    background: linear-gradient(
      168deg,
      var(--color-cream) 0%,
      var(--color-cream-light) 50%,
      var(--color-cream) 100%
    );
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl) 140px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .mission-inner {
    position: relative;
  }

  .mission-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-md);
  }

  .mission-heading {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    line-height: 1.3;
    max-width: 860px;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .mission-accent {
    width: 48px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--color-orange);
    border-radius: 2px;
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xl);
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .mission-body-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
